<h1>Delete Genre</h1>

Please ensure the genre you wish to delete is not tied with a game!

<p>Please pick a genre to delete</p>
<!--This form lists each genre currently in the database, and allows selection of one to delete.
  It returns the id of the selected genre, named "genre[delete_id]". 
  Sends a call to the "/genre_delete_from_database" receiver -->
<form action="/genre_delete_from_database">
  <select name="genre[delete_id]">
    <% @genre.each do |genre| %>
      <option value="<%= genre.id %>"><%= genre.name %></option>
    <% end %>
  </select>
  
  <button type="input">I'm sure, delete genre</button>
</form>

<p><a href="/home">Go to home page</a></p>